      "rationale": "CFD predictions of the relative hemolysis index (RH) were compared against FDA experimental measurements for all 5 operating points. The maximum deviation was 11.2%, within the 15% acceptance band. All predicted RH values were below 1.0, confirming non-inferiority to the predicate device. Gradation 2 requirements are satisfied."
